# ---- backend-dawn ----
# Third-party jars are declared in backend-dawn/dawn.toml's [java-deps] and fetched
# from Maven by `dawn build`, which copies them here next to the jar. Build output,
# not source — dawn.toml is the single source of truth for their versions.
backend-dawn/lib/

